# <%= current_page.data.title %>
Welcome to the Data Platform Services documentation hub! This is your one-stop shop for all things related to our service area, including architecture, ways of working, and more.

## About Data Platform Services

You can find out more about our service area on [MOJ People Finder](https://peoplefinder.service.gov.uk/teams/data-platform-services).

### Our teams

We have 2 squads working on Data Platform Services:

- Squad 1: responsible for the core infrastructure of Analytical Platform
- Squad 2: responsible for Find MOJ data and Create a Derived Table (CaDeT)

Both squads are working on the new Justice Data Platform.

